item.description: 5th Annual Charity Dyno Day dynojet logo What: 5th Annual Charity Dyno Day When: Saturday, September 17th, 11am - 3pm Where: Seacoast Sport Cycle It's time for our annual Charity Dyno Day! This year in benefit of Autism Speaks. Whatever your bike (or scooter!), you're invited. A $20 donation enters you into the contest. Prizes and awards to the most... and the least... horsepower in each class! We'll also have specials on accessories apparel all day long. The grill will be hot with plenty of food and drink. Have some fun and show everyone what you've got! Proceeds Benefit Autism Speaks
item.name: 5th Annual Charity Dyno Day
